node.text:
Our moment of choice is at hand. There has never been a more urgent moment for humanity to come together in synergy and collectively choose to hold the greatest vision of what we can be and do together, to lead with our hearts and co-create new possibilities that will offer us hope for our future.
This uplifting and timely book with 43 of the world's brightest evolutionary leaders is a call to action, offering evolutionary visions, resources and practical steps to help us navigate this moment of choice and amplify the movement for global transformation, upon which our future depends.

Get your copy of Our Moment of Choice here: https://bit.ly/ourmomentofchoice #OurMomentOfChoice #OMOM #Choice #GreggBraden #WisdomTraditions

node.text:
It's not a secret that our world is changing. Change isn't always easy, especially when you haven't been prepared for the kinds of changes that we are experiencing today. My goal is to help you embrace change in a healthy way so you can move forward with more resilience and confidence. 

That's why I created my all-new online course Radical Resilience that begins on Monday, July 13, 2020.

During this course, I will guide you through the new discoveries, the rock-solid science, and the proven techniques, to create powerful resilience in every aspect of your life. You'll experience six 60-minute workshops, where you will learn how to awaken and maintain resilience in your life! PLUS! you'll get to join me for three LIVE 30-minute Q&A forums.

If you're interested in joining me you can learn more and register at the link in my Bio or go to www.radicalresilience.greggbraden.com

I look forward to spending the next 3-weeks with you and sharing this information that I know will help you through all of life's challenges. #radicalresilience #resilience #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions 

#RadicalResilience #resilience #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions

node.text:
I’m thrilled to share that my latest book, The Wisdom Codes, is the recipient of the Nautilus Award, which spotlights better books for a better world.

The Wisdom Codes is perfect as a pocket guide, a reference for spiritual study, or a gift to someone you love, this elegant, compact book contains Wisdom Codes that cut to the core of life’s greatest tests, most challenging demands, and hardest lessons. You’ll find chapters devoted to healing from loss and grief, facing your unspoken fears, finding certainty in the face of uncertain choices, and finding forgiveness, as well as ancient parables that offer a “fast track” to unraveling life’s deepest mysteries.

Each Wisdom Code-distilled from a quote, a scripture passage, or a parable-is accompanied by a brief discussion of what the code means, why it’s important, and how to apply it in your life.

Click the link in my Bio to learn more about the Wisdom Codes and get your copy: https://bit.ly/thewisdomcodesamz

Thank you for your continued support of my work through the years. I hope this book helps to continue your journey of well-being and conscious awareness.

#twc #thewisdomcodes #nautilusawards #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions

node.text:
I want to invite you to join me for a special two-day workshop in Pheonix, AZ. Pure Human: Ignite on October 6-7, 2021.

The link is in my Bio @gregg.braden

During this workshop, I will lead you through some of the most recent discoveries merging science and spirituality in the alchemy of the human heart.

This program is designed to give you the maximum opportunity to do the deeper work that is the focus of our time together.

Our intention is to provide a nurturing, healing and sacred space, to assist you in your journey to raise your consciousness, expand your awareness, and access more of your innate abilities.

Highlights of This Program Include:

* Teach you how to access and program your body’s multiple operating systems to self-regulate the biology of your immune system, stem cells, regeneration and longevity enzymes and more, On-Demand, by accessing your innate epigenetic codes.
* The new discoveries and techniques to self-regulate the biology of your body, including how to choose cyclic aging rather than linear aging to up-regulate gene expression and DNA longevity!
* Understanding nature’s three principles that reveal the power that is available to us in relationships, health, healing and everyday life.
* A special segment dedicated to Fractal Time:
* Multiple opportunities over two days to learn, develop and fine-tune your skills of deep intuition, heart intelligence and biological self-regulation.

Much, much more!

I look forward to seeing you there!

node.text:
I want to take a moment to remember two of the most incredible and loving people to walk this earth and two of my dear friends. I am honored and grateful for the years I was able to teach along side Louise Hay and Dr. Wayne Dyer. They left a special imprint and helped millions of people change their lives and reach their highest potential. If you followed Louise and Wayne closely I would love for you to share your favorite memories, stories, and quotes that inspired you the most. You can leave them here in the comments.

#louisehay #waynedyer #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions #louiseandwayne
